commit message:
Add configurability, refactor a lot and change the graphics.

Now published on Android Market. :)

Remove unnecessary ldpi icons.

Android scales down hdpi icons 50% for ldpi devices. Also, they're not that common nowadays.

Redrawn, vector based graphics.

Also adds xxhdpi and xxxhdpi icons (requires API v16 and v18, respectively, hence no Gingerbread style icons there).
Bump version, target Android SDK v19.
Move preferences.xml to a more 'correct' location.
Change default action to 'Open WiFi Settings'.

Merge pull request #1 from svetlemodry/master

Czech translation created
